{"id": 1160, "genre": 1000, "title": "在这届奥运会，你听到了哪些理性的声音？", "description": "除了“更高、更快、更强”，你还看到了哪些“更智慧”？（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 10296, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160811113218aqIf1oGCjW3iOA9l.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-11T17:00:07Z", "questions": [{"id": 1046, "title": "在这届奥运会，你听到了哪些理性的声音？", "content": "在这届奥运会，你听到了哪些理性的声音？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 106287, "content": "敢于表达个性的运动员不再被视为叛逆，反而还有点萌", "image": "img/option/option/20160810182742psdzAOueqUS01nfl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 106289, "content": "即使没拿到好的名次，拼尽全力同样得到赞美", "image": "img/option/option/20160810182621qS0NPKngE8cW5dy6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 106293, "content": "相较于竞技成绩，运动员的健康状况更值得关注", "image": "img/option/option/201608101829106JYALCrMfqickvo7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 106296, "content": "不再只局限于奖牌，更关注运动趣味本身", "image": "img/option/option/20160810183025ilSxk583Un7s4uyE.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 106297, "content": "相较于“国家/民族”，如今对运动员的喜欢更多是被个人魅力圈粉", "image": "img/option/option/20160810182554TyLWHqf7Cam5h4e8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 106298, "content": "不以受害者心态去证明自己所谓“强大”", "image": "img/option/option/20160810183230Pok4E7fL8qZ3WBCj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 106311, "content": "视角更开放，不再觉得举国体制是最合理的", "image": "img/option/option/20160810183403IFJyjbgnCa6Vmkro.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 106669, "content": "面对争议和谣言先看科普，反对不理性", "image": "img/option/option/20160811180125n98uqi4hvdMW1BZ2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}